                    <p class="text-black text-base leading-normal md:text-xl lg:text-2xl md:leading-snug font-light pb-4 md:pb-7">A few lines here about remote work, WFH, company policy with workiung days vs days off etc.</p>
                    <p class="text-black text-base leading-normal md:text-xl lg:text-2xl md:leading-snug font-light ">We know that not everyone can or wants to work from our office in Bangalore. As of 2019, we have two fully remote employees on staff, and plan to hire more. If there's a way we can make your workday with nilenso more comfortable or fun, we'll do it. If we can help you with something else, just ask. We'll try.</p>
                </div>
